Title: Lubriderm Daily Moisture Moisturizer SPF 15 13.5 oz (3 Pack)
Body (HTML): Lubriderm Daily Moisture Hydrating Body Lotion with Broad Spectrum SPF 15 Sunscreen and Vitamin B5 helps moisturize and protect your skin from the sun's harmful rays. From a dermatologist-developed brand, this daily lotion is clinically shown to moisturize for 24 hours, so skin stays hydrated all day long. It contains vitamin B5 and essential moisturizers to hydrate skin, and broad spectrum SPF 15 to help provide protection from the sun's harmful UVA and UVB rays. The lotion is non-greasy and fast-absorbing for a clean feel.
